    <title>Emergent Planning in Multi-Agent Reinforcement Learning</title>
    <summary>  We present a novel approach to emergent planning in multi-agent
reinforcement learning systems. Our method combines hierarchical
task decomposition with learned communication protocols to enable
coordinated behaviour in complex environments.
</summary>
